OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThames Water needs         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'substantial' sums of money
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK's largest water company Thames  
OL,6, Water will need "substantial sums of   
OL,7, money" to stabilise its finances, the  
OL,8, water regulator has said.              
OL,10,FOfwat boss David Black said talks      
OL,11,Fbetween the firm and investors to raise
OL,12,Fthe extra funding were continuing.     
OL,14,FThe water firm, which serves a quarter 
OL,15,Fof the UK population, is billions in   
OL,16,Fdebt and is under pressure to fix its  
OL,17,Ffinances after fears it could collapse.
OL,19,FThere have been calls to nationalise   
OL,20,Fthe firm after its boss quit last week.
